      "content": "that seems a bit biased though. you're saying the \"human right\" side is based on ethics while the other side is just complaining about bureaucracy. isn't the concern about government control and economic efficiency just as valid an argument as the ethical one? it feels like you're dismissing the economic side as less \"grounded.\"",
